= Ruby FileMagic Library Binding

== Summary

ruby-filemagic provides a ruby binding to GNU libmagic.


== Prerequisites

GNU file package to provide libmagic (tested with 5.04).


== Build and install

To build either:

    rake build

or run:

    ruby extconf.rb
    make

To install (non-gem) either:

    rake install

or run:

    make install


== Gem

To create a gem, build as above then either:

    rake gem

or run:

    gem build ruby-filemagic.gemspec


== Tests

To run the unit tests:

    rake test

or run:

    ruby test/regress.rb


== Examples

    require 'filemagic'
    magic = FileMagic.new
    puts magic.file('/tmp/foo')
    magic.close


